## 解説

N 個の整数を読みながら、`x % 2 == 0`（2 で割り切れる＝偶数）のものを数えます。

```java
int count = 0;
for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
    int x = sc.nextInt();
    if (x % 2 == 0) count++;
}
System.out.println(count);
```

answer_code:
import java.util.Scanner;

class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        int n = sc.nextInt();
        int count = 0;
        for (int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            int x = sc.nextInt();
            if (x % 2 == 0) count++;
        }
        System.out.println(count);
    }
}
